name: FACELESS MUTANT ARTIFACT - EYE OF CRHONUS
description:
As the Faceless Mutant Series (FMS) goes, the artifacts from the titans are valuable to help the other FMS release to their cages.

Far from our galaxy, FM treants are isolated to prevent their extinction due to the illegal activities of loggers on earth. this artifact (Eye of Kronos) helps the FM treant to travel go back to earth and bring back the other tree creatures and treants to live peacefully in the forests.
-To be continued...
